<p>i cant really decide if i should change the name or not to something else other then human mp3 player. like maybe call it the human radio station player<br />
<a href="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/longjumpingman">http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/longjumpingman</a><br />
and also i want to make sure this idea isnt already taken<br />
<strong>Seeking Greenlights:</strong> Yes</p>
<p><strong>Page Type:</strong> SCP Article</p>
<p><strong>Elevator Pitch:</strong> someone who was a regular person now considered something dangerous due to his ability to record audio with his mind and play the way he heard it out of his mouth sounding exactly the same.<br />
<strong>Central Narrative:</strong> a person who was once a regular man woke up and looked in the mirror to discover a weird circular device stuck in his neck he tried to pull it off but couldnt.<br />
he tried to speak but then discovered he could sound exactly like singers of popular songs after singing scatmans world and even able to sing instrumental songs with his throat.<br />
for 3 months he kept this secret from friends and family.<br />
eventually the Foundation caught wind of this after investigating news papers from the subjects hometown about his ability and then later caught him after he was heard singing Michael Jacksons song thriller.</p>
<p><strong>Hook/Attention-Grabber:</strong> a person whos able to sound exactly like singers and musicans while also being able to sing instrumental music that sounds like a CD player playing music and also being able to record sounds and play the sounds with his own mind</p>
